In [30]:
#creating dataframe
import pandas as pd
data = pd.DataFrame(columns=['Product_ID', 'PName', 'Price','Image','URL'])
In [31]:
#Appending all the values avaiable on the page to the dataframe
for i in divs:
    id = re.search('\d+',i.get('class')[-1]).group()
    name = i.find('h5', class_='ProductDetails').select('a')[0].get_text()
    img = i.find('img', class_='img-responsive').get("data-src")
    url = i.select('a')[0].get("href")
    price = i.find('div', class_='ActualPrice').get_text()
    price= re.search('\d+,\d+',price).group()
    
    #appending to the dataframe
    data = data.append({'Product_ID': id, 'PName': name, 'Price': price, 'Image':img, 'URL':url}, ignore_index=True)
